    "body": "This commit introduces a curated 2048-word Bangla wordlist for BIP39. The wordlist was generated from the Wiktionary dataset, strictly following BIP39 rules:\r\n- Words are between 4 and 8 characters long.\r\n- First 4 characters uniquely identify the word.\r\n- Excluded complex characters (e.g. 'রেফ', 'খন্ড ত') and complex conjunctions for ease of typing on phonetic keyboards.",
